msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 7. Usulomasutta → usu-kāraṇiyo (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Usulomasutta "
msgstr "7. Arrow Hairs "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.7:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ usulomaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man whose body hairs were arrows flying through the air. "

msgctxt "sn19.7:1.2"
msgid "Tassa te usū uppatitvā uppatitvā tasseva kāye nipatanti. "
msgstr "And those arrows kept rising up and falling on his body "

msgctxt "sn19.7:1.3"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.7:1.4"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe kāraṇiko ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That being used to be a torturer right here in Rājagaha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.7:1.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

